Hodder Faith is the UK’s leading Christian publisher, home to authors Philip Yancey, Joyce Meyer and RT Kendell amongst others. They continue to publish the NIV Bible in its various formats and to break new ground with books like Wm. Paul Young’s The Shack (2008).
Flipback[edit]
In 2011, Hodder launched a wholly new print format for books, the flipback. Printed on Bible paper, and designed to replicate the traditional print reading experience in an edition not much bigger than an iPhone.
