Hodder & Stoughton, Coronet, Hodder Faith, John Murray, Mulholland, Quercus, Saltyard, Sceptre, Two Roads


Official website
hodder.co.uk


Hodder & Stoughton is a British publishing house, now an imprint of Hachette.



